feat: add noxuslab check (review gate) and provenance-aware diff

noxuslab check <file> bundles dry-run + diff vs server (auto-extracts
workflow id from provenance header) + last-trace summary, giving a
single safe-to-commit/PR gate. noxuslab diff <file> now also accepts
the file alone when provenance is present. README documents the
pull -> run -> trace -> check -> commit -> PR -> push loop.
